<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to WXJourney</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg-deep-blue: #0a0e29; 
      --panel-bg: #0d1233; 
      --neon-green: #39ff14; 
      --action-red: #FD3777; 
      --hot-purple: #BF00FF; 
      --electric-cyan: #00f0ff; 
      --electric-purple: #8a2be2; 
      --tron-orange: #ff8d00; 
      --plus-lime: #CCFF00; 
      --country-plum: #920075; 
      --date-mint: #00ffa3; 
      --text-main: #f0f0f0; 
    }

    body {
      background-color: var(--bg-deep-blue);
      color: var(--text-main);
      font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px; 
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    h1 {
      color: var(--electric-cyan);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 6px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      border-bottom: 3px solid var(--plus-lime);
      padding-bottom: 10px;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      text-align: center;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .controls-container {
      background-color: var(--panel-bg);
      padding: 25px; 
      border: 2px solid var(--electric-purple); 
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 500px; 
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .intro-text {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }

    .intro-text p {
      margin: 10px 0;
    }

    h2 {
      color: var(--date-mint);
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--electric-purple);
      padding-bottom: 5px;
      margin-top: 0;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
    }

    .instruction-list {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 15px;
    }

    .instruction-card {
      background-color: var(--bg-deep-blue);
      border: 1px solid var(--electric-purple); 
      padding: 15px; 
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .instruction-title {
      color: var(--hot-purple);
      font-weight: 900;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--electric-purple);
      padding-bottom: 4px;
    }

    /* Target Highlight Colors based on your file's CSS variables */
    .color-blue { color: var(--electric-cyan); font-weight: bold; }
    .color-green { color: var(--date-mint); font-weight: bold; }
    .color-yellow { color: var(--plus-lime); font-weight: bold; }
    .color-orange { color: var(--tron-orange); font-weight: bold; }
    .color-red { color: var(--action-red); font-weight: bold; }
    .color-plum { color: var(--country-plum); font-weight: bold; }

  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="controls-container">
    <h1>Welcome to WXJourney</h1>
    
    <div class="intro-text">
      <p>WXJourney allows you to create a custom forecast by date and location.</p>
      <p><small>Forecast data is provided by the <span class="color-plum">ECMWF</span>.</small></p>
    </div>

    <h2>How to use:</h2>
    
    <div class="instruction-list">
      <div class="instruction-card">
        <span class="instruction-title">Add a record</span>
        Enter a location into the blue <span class="color-blue">[location picker]</span>. Select a date using the green <span class="color-green">[date picker]</span>. Press the yellow <span class="color-yellow">[+]</span> button to create the record.
      </div>

      <div class="instruction-card">
        <span class="instruction-title">Refresh forecast</span>
        Use the <span class="color-red">[refresh]</span> to update forcasts. New forecasts data is available at 00:00 UTC and 12:00 UTC.
      </div>

      <div class="instruction-card">
        <span class="instruction-title">Edit a record</span>
        Change the date of an existing record to update the date. Records automatically sort chronologically.
      </div>

      <div class="instruction-card">
        <span class="instruction-title">Delete a record</span>
        Press the orange <span class="color-orange">[X]</span> button in an existing record.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>